# FormValidation Demo üöÄ

A production-ready form validation demo built with React Native, Formik, and Yup. This demo showcases professional form handling with real-time validation, password strength meters, and a polished UI.

![Demo Preview](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-live-green)
![React Native](https://img.shields.io/badge/React%20Native-0.72-blue)
![Formik](https://img.shields.io/badge/Formik-2.4-purple)
![Yup](https://img.shields.io/badge/Yup-1.3-yellow)

## ‚ú® Features

### üìã Form Validation
- Real-time field validation with instant feedback
- Password strength meter with visual indicators
- Phone number formatting and validation
- Age verification (18+ years)
- Email format validation

### üé® UI/UX Features
- Clean, modern design with Material Design icons
- Responsive layout for all screen sizes
- Loading states and animations
- Keyboard-aware scrolling
- Touch-friendly inputs
- Error highlighting with icons

### üîí Security Features
- Secure password input with visibility toggle
- Password confirmation validation
- Terms & Conditions acceptance requirement
- Input sanitization

### üìä Validation Rules
| Field | Requirements |
|-------|-------------|
| **Full Name** | 3-50 characters, letters and spaces only |
| **Email** | Valid email format, required |
| **Phone** | Exactly 10 digits, auto-formatted |
| **Date of Birth** | Must be 18+ years old |
| **Password** | 8+ chars, uppercase, number, special char |
| **Terms** | Must be accepted |

## üöÄ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 16+
- npm or yarn
- iOS Simulator (for iOS) or Android Studio (for Android)

### Installation
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/ewuwise/FormValidation.git
cd FormValidation

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the development server
npm run web
# or
npm run ios
npm run android
```

